<HEADLINE>
HOLLYWOOD GETS IT WRONG IN `MAGNOLIA'
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By Dennis McCarthy  
 c.1999 Los Angeles Daily News  
<TEXT>
<P>
   If ever a movie should come with a neon warning label, it's the
film ``Magnolia.''
</P>
<P>
   ``Warning _ if you've believed all the hype and think you're
about to see a movie depicting real life in Los Angeles' San
