<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-12-17 12:04 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1839 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u v HEARST-FEATURE-BUDGET &LR;      12-17 0812
</HEADER>
