c.1999 Cox News Service  
<TEXT>
<P>
   AUSTIN, Texas _
</P>
<P>
   www.officialstuff.com _ For the sports fan who gets to do
everything but go to the bowl games, officialstuff.com offers a
unique kind of gift _ official programs and commemorative books to
more than 50 big events, including Super Bowls, races and tennis
tournaments. While it may not be as fun as being there, you can
always keep a little bit of sporting glory on your bookshelf.
