that inner board game player at areyougame.com, an e-tailer
specializing in games and puzzles, a $2 billion a year industry. In
``kid vote,'' youngsters can vote on their favorite games. And for
gift shoppers, you can browse by age category.
</P>
<P>
   Must buy: The old standby, Twister, for $17.95 including
shipping.
