<P>
   MIDEAST-TRAVEL _ JERUSALEM _ A review of what's going on at the
millennium sites. At Armageddon, the place where the battle to end
all battles is supposed to occur, the Israelis have fixed up the
park that is there. At the Church of the Holy Sepulchre, where
orthodox Christians believe Christ was crucified, the five
bickering denominations in charge are trying to agree on where to
place an exit door _ the first change in the church in years. In
Bethlehem, the Palestinians have rebuilt the plaza and torn down
the ugly old British jail next to the church. (Kaplow, Cox News
Service).
