not the politicians who perform in them but the people who put them
on. By David Nyhan.
</P>
<P>
   JACKSON-COLUMN (Undated) _ Demanding that students pass rigorous
standardized tests with substandard educations is unfair, if not
illegal. By Derrick Jackson.
</P>
<P>
   VENNOCHI-COLUMN (Undated) _ The heartbreak of six deaths and 17
fatherless children does not necessarily add up to a manslaughter
conviction. By Joan Vennochi.
</P>
