<SLUG> BC-TIMES-WORCESTER2-BOS </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
TIMES CO. TO REDUCE WORK FORCE IN WORCESTER BY 30 JOBS 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  
 By CHRIS REIDY  
 c.1999 The Boston Globe  
 
<TEXT>
